 genus of the family; -<em>aceae</em> ending to denote a family; N.L. fem. pl. n. <em>Segniliparaceae</em> the <em>Segniliparus</em> family).</s></p><p class="description"><s>Cells are rod-shaped; no branching.</s><s>Aerobic.</s><s>Strongly acid-fast.</s><s>Produce multiple chemical functional groups of high-molecular-mass, non-polar, mycolic acids.</s><s>The 16S rRNA gene sequences and HPLC mycolic acid patterns are as indicated for the genus <em>Segniliparus</em>.</s><s>The family contains the type genus <em>Segniliparus</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>